---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="How to Add Custom Images - Hunger Games Simulator" 
  description="Learn how to add and customize tribute images in the Hunger Games Simulator to create a more personalized gaming experience."
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-center mb-12 mt-8">
      How to Add Custom Images to Hunger Games Simulator
    </h1>
    
    <p class="text-center text-white/60 mb-16">
      Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-12">
      <!-- 介绍部分 -->
      <div class="bg-secondary-light rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mb-4">
          Customizing tribute images can make your Hunger Games simulation more personal and engaging. This guide will walk you through the process of adding custom images for your tributes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 步骤1 -->
      <div class="bg-secondary-light rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Step 1: Prepare Your Images</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-white/80">Before adding custom images, make sure your images meet these requirements:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-white/80 ml-4">
            <li>Square aspect ratio (1:1) recommended</li>
            <li>File size under 2MB</li>
            <li>Supported formats: JPG, PNG, WebP</li>
            <li>Recommended resolution: 200x200 pixels</li>
            <li>Upload your images to <a href="https://imgur.com/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Imgur</a> and get the direct URL</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 步骤2 -->
      <div class="bg-secondary-light rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Step 2: Access the Customization Page</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-white/80">To add custom images:</p>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-white/80 ml-4">
            <li>Start from the home page</li>
            <li>Click "Start Hunger Games"</li>
            <li>On the Reaping page, click "Customize Tribute"</li>
            <li><a href="/customize" class="text-primary hover:underline">You can click here to go to the Customize Tribute page</a></li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 步骤3 -->
      <div class="bg-secondary-light rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Step 3: Add Your Images</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-white/80">There are way to add custom images:</p>
          
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Method 1: Direct URL Input</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-white/80 ml-4">
            <li>Paste the imgur URL into the tribute's image field</li>
            <li>The image will automatically update if the URL is valid</li>
          </ul>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 注意事项 -->
      <div class="bg-secondary-light rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Important Notes</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-white/80 ml-4">
            <li>Make sure your image URLs are from reliable sources and permanently accessible</li>
            <li>If an image fails to load, a default avatar will be used</li>
            <li>Custom images are stored locally and will persist until you start a new game</li>
            <li>Respect copyright and only use images you have permission to use</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 相关链接 -->
      <div class="bg-secondary-light rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Related Links</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-white/80 ml-4">
            <li>
              <a href="/reaping" class="text-primary hover:underline">Start a New Game</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/customize" class="text-primary hover:underline">Customize Tributes</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://x.com/liarpzu" class="text-primary hover:underline">Follow us on X for Updates</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout> 